r Party</span><span class=\"c3\">: </span><span class=\"c8 c11\"><a class=\"c1\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.google.com/maps/dir//274%2BChebomnicon%2BRd,%2BLa%2BPointe,%2BWI%2B54850/@46.7794599,-90.7907174,16z/data%3D!4m8!4m7!1m0!1m5!1m1!1s0x52a9032153011409:0x302251812ff359ed!2m2!1d-90.78634!2d46.77946&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1531291222169000\">Tom’s Burndown Cafe, 274 Chebomnicon Rd, La Pointe, WI 54850</a></span><span class=\"c3\"><br><br></span><span class=\"c13\"><br></span><span class=\"c8 c9\">General Information<br><br></span><span class=\"c4\">The ceremony will be held on the rocks at Big Bay Point at 2 pm, rain or shine; a map of &nbsp;Big Bay State Park and directions to the point are linked in the sidebar. A shuttle van will be available to transport people from the town of La Pointe to the state park in order to avoid day permit fees for guests. Potential lodging options and the &nbsp;car ferry schedule are in the sidebar links as well. An after party will be held at Tom’s Burndown Cafe in the town of La Point, starting loosely at 5pm and lasting...well we won’t worry about that. There are several restaurants nearby, but no group meal is planned. Children and Plus 1s welcome! <br><br>We realize that the travel and time involved may not be feasible for everyone, and that’s ok. Thank you for being our family and friends, whether you are able to attend or not. <br><br>~Please no gifts, we’re old and have lots of stuff. Your presence is the best gift~</span></p><p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c4\"></span></p><p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c6\">Hotels</span></p><p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c5\"><a class=\"c1\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://hotelguides.com/wisconsin/bayfield-wi-hotels.html&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1531291222170000\">https://hotelguides.com/wisconsin/bayfield-wi-hotels.html</a></span><span class=\"c3 c7\">&nbsp;Bayfield and Ashland </span></p><p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c6\"></span></p><p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c6\">Lodging</span></p><p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c5\"><a class=\"c1\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.madelineislandvacations.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1531291222170000\">http://www.madelineislandvacations.com/</a></span><span class=\"c3 c7\">&nbsp;La Pointe Hotel Listings</span></p><p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c5\"><a class=\"c1\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.ferrylandingsuites.net/&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1531291222171000\">http://www.ferrylandingsuites.net/</a></span><span class=\"c3 c7\">&nbsp;Ferry Landing Suites</span></p><p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c5\"><a class=\"c1\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.madisland.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1531291222171000\">https://www.madisland.com/</a></span><span class=\"c3 c7\">&nbsp;The Inn on Madeline Island</span></p><p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c6\"></span></p><p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c6\">Camping</span></p><p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c5\"><a class=\"c1\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://dnr.wi.gov/topic/parks/name/bigbay/&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1531291222171000\">https://dnr.wi.gov/topic/parks/name/bigbay/</a></span><span class=\"c3 c7\">&nbsp; Big Bay State Park</span></p><p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c5\"><a class=\"c1\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.bigbaytownpark.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1531291222171000\">http://www.bigbaytownpark.com/</a></span><span class=\"c3 c7\">&nbsp;City Park and Camping</span></p><p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c6\"></span></p><p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c6\">Madeline Island Ferry</span></p><p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c5\"><a class=\"c1\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://madferry.com/ferry-schedule&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1531291222172000\">https://madferry.com/ferry-schedule</a></span><span class=\"c3 c7\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c6\">Island Transportation</span></p><p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c5\"><a class=\"c1\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.motion-to-go.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=153129